content.p:
Also approves the establishment, effective 1 January 2026, under section 24, Human rights, of the proposed programme budget for 2026, of 13 posts, of which 10 are for the Independent Investigative Mechanism for Afghanistan and 3 are for the Office of the High Commissioner, to support the activities mandated by the Human Rights Council in its resolutions 58/13 of 3 April 2025,
See Official Records of the General Assembly, Eightieth Session, Supplement No. 53 (A/80/53), chap. V, sect. A. 60/2 and 60/14 of 6 October 2025 and 60/20 of 7 October 2025;
Ibid., Supplement No. 53A (A/80/53/Add.1), chap. III, sect. A.
